				<div class="newsD-article-title">
					<h2>汉中市铁路中心医院 6月招聘医学检验工作人员拟聘人选公示</h2>
					<p style="font-size:14px;">汉中市第一医院（汉中市妇女儿童医院）官网&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-size:14px;">2024-07-02 08:08:27</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;来源：&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;阅读量：11221</p>
				</div>
				<div class="newsD-article-content">
					<p>
						<p><br/></p><p style="text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:center;line-height:40px"><span style=";font-family:方正小标宋简体;font-size:29px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:center;line-height:40px"><span style=";font-family:方正小标宋简体;font-size:29px">汉中市</span><span style=";font-family:方正小标宋简体;font-size:29px">铁路</span><span style=";font-family:方正小标宋简体;font-size:29px">中心医院</span></p><p style="text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:center;line-height:40px"><span style=";font-family:方正小标宋简体;font-size:29px">6月</span><span style=";font-family:方正小标宋简体;font-size:29px">招聘医学检验工作人员拟聘人选公示</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:40px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 21px;background: #FFFFFF">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 仿宋;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 21px;background: #FFFFFF">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:仿宋">根据汉中市铁路中心医院</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">2024年6月3日发布的《汉中市铁路中心医院招聘医学检验专业人员的公告》及6月13日发布的《汉中市铁路中心医院6月招聘医学检验专业人员成绩通报》</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 21px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:仿宋">，经招聘笔试、面试、体检、考察后，第一名邹蓉放弃此次聘用资格，按顺序递补下一名，最终确定拟聘人选为：黄金辉、周妮。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:40px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 21px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:仿宋">现面向社会进行公示</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">,公示时间:2024年7月2日至7月6日。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:40px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 21px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:仿宋">咨询电话：</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">0916-2212561（人事科）</span></span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:40px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 21px;background: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family:仿宋">监督电话：</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">0916-2692140</span></span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:40px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 21px;background: #FFFFFF">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:40px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:40px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 37px; text-align: right; line-height: 40px;"><span style="background-color: #FFFFFF; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px; letter-spacing: 0px; text-indent: 43px;">汉中市铁路中心医院人事科</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 37px; text-align: right; line-height: 40px;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; background-color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 21px; letter-spacing: 0px; text-indent: 85px;">2024年7月2日&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:33px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 21px;background: #FFFFFF">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>					</p>
					<!--<a href="#">返回</a>-->
				</div>
				<div class="expert_details_bottom">
